name: Warung D'Dagan
address: Banjar Salak, Batumadeg Klod, 6FPW+CC9, Batumadeg, Kec. Nusa Penida, Kabupaten Klungkung, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1:
Nice little Warung in the middle of nowhere.
Food is very good, portions big and prices very decent.
A good spot to fuel up you energy before further exploring.
